label: 539f6fbbec4f024411ecd21b
name: SCHEDULE SASB-6 SEASONAL AGRICULTURAL SERVICE
description:
APPLICABILITY:
Applicable to agricultural production including storage, drying, curing, handling, grain mill and oil mill operations and other agricultural related applications where at least Eighty percent (80%) of the annual kWh consumption occurs in any six (6) consecutive month period. The customer will be responsible to the Company for any additional cost of installing and removing any equipment required to control, meter or deliver this service. This electric service shall be delivered at one (1) point, at one (1) standard voltage
and metered at or compensated to that voltage and is available to any customer with an actual demand of less than 500 kW.
